**$8,000–$12,000 total — Best Versatile:** [Channel Set Accent in 14K white gold at $3,600](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-engagement-ring-with-channel-set-diamond-accent-in-14k-white-gold-item-296630?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) + a 1.00ct natural pear (G VS2, GIA Excellent, ~$3,500–$4,200) = complete ring $7,100–$7,800. The channel accent diamonds add sparkle from the band without competing with the pear center. White gold is correct for G-color. This tier gives you a 1ct natural pear in a bezel setting with meaningful additional design.

**$12,000+ — Best Statement:** [Emerald Side Stone in platinum at $5,260](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-set-emerald-cut-side-stone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-304637?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) + a 1.50ct natural pear (F VS2, GIA Excellent, ~$7,500–$9,500) = complete ring $12,760–$14,760. Platinum bezel wall with emerald side stones is the definitive architectural statement in the pear diamond category. Maximum protection, maximum design, maximum longevity.

